558
00:46:35,285 --> 00:46:37,378
Apa yang kamu pikirkan?

559
00:46:37,378 --> 00:46:38,994
Apakah kamu sudah selesai?

560
00:46:42,282 --> 00:46:45,749
Jangan bersikap terlalu dekat denganku, Kang Bang Geul.

561
00:46:54,020 --> 00:46:55,540
Tetap tenang.

562
00:46:56,594 --> 00:46:59,394
Tunggu bukti yang kuat.

563
00:47:00,988 --> 00:47:02,495
Tetap tenang.

564
